<br>
I'm Christian and an avid RPG'er and I have had this fight with lots of folks who hold the same views as the apologetics site Illanae posted. As an aside, logosresourcepages isn't a very credible apologetics site. Legalism at its finest...er worst.<br>
<br>
My argument with the people like that always goes back to J.R.R. Tolkien and C.S. Lewis.  Both of them very devout Christians. C.S. Lewis himself has been labeled as arguably the greatest Christian writer of our time. Both of these great Christian men wrote high fantasy. C.S. Lewis wrote &quot;The Chronicles of Narnia&quot; and Tolkien wrote...hmmm, well he wrote some books too I'd imagine! <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START ;) --><img src=http://jens-smileys.netfirms.com/wink.gif ALT=";)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  <br>
<br>
It's undeniable that Tolkien's mythos has directly inspired what eventually became D&amp;D. So for sites like that to judge D&amp;D and the genre associated with it, is silly imo. It's actually kinda funny to listen to someone curse Harry Potter and in the same breath praise The Lord of the Rings. I just roll my eyes and go about my business....usually.<br>
<br>
Pokemon, RPG's, games, whatever are just things. They aren't good or bad. People make them good or bad.  If one of these or any other &quot;thing&quot; completely dominates a person's life to the extent that they neglect everything else, then ok, it's probably bad...for that person.<br>
<br>
Anyway, food for thought..... <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://jens-smileys.netfirms.com/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->   <p></p><i>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub141.ezboard.com/beverquestpeople.showUserPublicProfile?gid=hojohominygrits>Hojo Hominygrits</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://members.cox.net/stmyers/eye.gif" BORDER=0> at: 12/2/02 9:20:37 am<br></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#77839D><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub141.ezboard.com/beverquestpeople.showUserPublicProfile?gid=drenon>Drenon</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://personal.bgsu.edu/~bedavis/megadre.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle><TABLE STYLE=filter:Glow(color=#63DE00,strength=4><TR><TD><center><font color=#000000> <b> Jolly Green Dagiant </center></TABLE></font> </b> <br> Member of<br>Wendy's Anonymous

